This is a list of all sure [[Genus|genera]], [[species]] and [[subspecies]] of the [[Family (biology)|subfamily]] '''[[Crotalinae]]''',<ref name="ITIS">{{ITIS |id=634394 |taxon=Crotalinae |accessdate=28 December 2007}}</ref> otherwise referred to as crotalines, pit vipers or pitvipers. It follows the [[Alpha taxonomy|taxonomy]] currently provided by [[Integrated Taxonomic Information System|ITIS]], which is based on the continuing work of Dr. Roy McDiarmid.<ref name="McD99">McDiarmid RW, Campbell JA, Touré T. 1999. Snake Species of the World: A Taxonomic and Geographic Reference, vol. 1. Herpetologists' League. 511 pp. {{ISBN|1-893777-00-6}} (series). {{ISBN|1-893777-01-4}} (volume).</ref>
